Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.71,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}ふぅふぅ らったった らったったった ふぅふぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:01.33,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}らったったらっぱ いぇーい いぇーい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}らったった らったったった ふぅふぅいぇい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:14.14,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}朝目が覚めたらもう昨日みたいな日常はなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:18.06,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}「ホントあぁもう…えっとどうしよう」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:24.98,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}ため息混じりに練るお菓子と妄想のレシピの中に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.28,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}恋心入っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:34.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}シフォンケーキにカスタード スコーンにクロテッドクリーム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:40.50,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}だけどやっぱこれっておかしいわ どうして私なんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:45.59,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}急にそんな事言い出して…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.71,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}あぁどうしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:52.30,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}君を好きになっちゃうかなんて分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:57.60,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}大切な人だなんてAh照れくさいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.40,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}君は真面目なトーンで好きってなんて言うでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.94,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}ちょっとドキッとしちゃうじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:09.24,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}なんて非日常的なレボリューション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:14.14,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}早晨醒來發覺過往的生活已經消失無蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:18.06,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}「真的嗎 那個…該怎麼辦呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:24.98,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}一邊嘆氣一邊做著點心和妄想的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.28,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}一不小心放入了戀愛的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:34.87,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}戚風蛋糕加上奶黃 司康餅佐上濃縮奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:40.50,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}但這果然有些奇怪 為什麼會選上了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:45.59,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}突然說出那種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.71,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}啊 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:52.30,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}雖然不知道會不會喜歡上你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:57.60,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}被你所如此看重真令人害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.40,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}你會認真的對我說著喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.94,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}這讓人心中小鹿亂撞不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:09.24,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}多麼非日常的革命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳不在了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}房間都收拾的乾乾淨淨的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}衣服和課本也都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}究竟是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難不成是回老家什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要緊的 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個人是不會什麼都不說就回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真回去的話一定會打招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他們可是懂禮貌的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肯定是有什麼急事出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說、說的也是呢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.52,0:02:19.49,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)}#12 你明白了嗎？ 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:19.49,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,470)\3c&HF2C855&\bord7}#12 你明白了嗎？ 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真安靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會是真的是回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\c&H654553&\shad0\fs30\pos(554,324)\frz2.938}和真白回山裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和白夜約會了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想問問去了哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聯絡不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發郵件也沒回信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}電話也一直打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是家裡有什麼事情回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道白夜他們家在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道大概的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼擔心的話就追上去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正學校也放假了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但、但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果擅自離家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人和媽媽都會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且 說不定真的是白夜他們有事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想這種時候耍個任性是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}畢竟你是未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去白夜他們老家也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 謝謝你 真由良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:57.77,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}木々をゆらしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:03.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}あたたかい風に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:10.82,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}少しまだ戸惑う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:17.00,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}臆病なわたし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.88,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}もっと近づけたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.17,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}きみに屆くのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.55,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}素直になれなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:35.39,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}からまわる 心の聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:44.61,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}いま気付いた この胸の奧で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:51.28,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}芽生えだした蕾がある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:58.12,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}ひとみ そらさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:04.75,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}見つけたい 芽生えた蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:14.93,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}歩いてく きみへ向かう道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:57.77,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}樹林搖擺不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:03.78,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}正因暖風吹拂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:10.82,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}尚有些許困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:17.00,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}如此膽小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:20.88,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}如果再接近你一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.17,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}真的能傳達給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.55,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}無法變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:35.39,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}徘徊不決的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:44.61,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}如今才注意到 胸口深處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:51.28,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}那漸漸萌芽的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:58.12,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}不要移開視線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:04.75,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}想去尋找 那萌發的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:14.93,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}我將踏上 去往你身邊的路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母親大人 姐姐大人 我是小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去白夜的老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想會在晚上前回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然聽媽媽的話回來是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以摘到這麼多春天的野菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼多的話小紅也會開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為她說過想嚐嚐我們這裡的野菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 開始下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我聽到小紅的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會吧 小紅應該在家裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好冷 我會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是從冬眠中醒來的熊之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅？！你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個突然不見就追過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們只是來摘野菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順便把我們的成績單拿給媽媽看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成績單？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成績單果然還是要給家長過目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 你們為什麼還把房間打掃的那麼乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}衣服和課本也都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}衣服是因為要換春裝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}教科書是因為升到二年級用不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想放回家裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 白夜不是發給小紅郵件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般這種時候都會在後面寫上「去去就來」「很快就回來」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道你沒看到我發的郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這附近沒有信號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別讓我這麼擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那麼擔心我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不只是我 姐姐大人和母親大人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 一放鬆怎麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}小紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 小紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼偏偏遇到暴風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然這裡可以避風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但如果不趕快讓小紅回家休息的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 你能抱著小紅跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能 不過這麼大的風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅會凍僵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去叫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白在這裡陪她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 你快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撐住啊 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜很快就會回來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 糟了 這樣下去火堆會滅掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的話應該可以去撿些柴火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我很快就回來 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我們走了哦 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要乖乖待在家裡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家 都漸漸離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不像母親大人和姐姐大人學習那麼優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不擅長運動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只會做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果秘密被別人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不能留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}傷疤的事 不想讓你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連白夜和真白都要離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又要丟下我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 撿樹枝花了一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不見了 在我去找薪柴的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趕快找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發著燒應該走不了太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要擔心 真白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們這麼多人肯定馬上就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦 要是小紅出了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是真白的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我能再早一點趕回來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個都冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找找看有沒有腳印之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是白夜的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅一定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…什麼時候到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次…趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體好點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖和起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在附近找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 是我讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時也像現在這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是白夜陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是說你的傷痕不是因為我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一開始就不用隱瞞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是被你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺你會很介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很介意 很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這麼重要的事情還是希望你別隱瞞我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就不用隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不是未婚夫妻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以後不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再也不會隱瞞你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}右眼看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能看到光線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是小紅的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和小紅在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰家的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們馬上去你那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這下放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良家公司的直升機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為小紅你失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我告訴了小紅的媽媽和紅緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我自己都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅和真白碳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒受傷吧 冷不冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓我們互相溫暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把責任都給冬天吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 你們兩個人在一起的時候有沒有發生什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什什什什…什麼事都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事…都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是兩個人在雪山上獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好浪漫的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣一來兩個人之間的感情不就一下子加深了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\pos(640,710)}那個表情算什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(640,670,640,710,402,777)}什麼什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說人家的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人你冷靜一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬你的聲音也很大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢走 注意安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}升到2年級還是跟真由良在一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的呢 白夜同學和真白醬也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家都在一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是你又使用能力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 你說啥呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下來 UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用UMA來贏得獨家新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉要是找到了未確認生物的話要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬和真白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到這張海報了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}摩克拉姆貝貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我現在主要以這個方向取材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有任何發現要聯絡我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬看到的不會是你吧 小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 倒不如說是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你朋友要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又不是UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是很出色又有歷史的一族呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰家是歷史悠久的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是UMA呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA UMA 呀 UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好大的UMA味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說別人是UMA的才是UMA呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先說UMA的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是你先說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新聞部好像是在收集UMA的情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明有比UMA好的特集呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹特集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是什麼校內報刊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特集 妹妹游泳大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}參賽隊是 親生妹妹和義理妹妹隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這個故事好像挺長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新學期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}春天將至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是還是一如既往的熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下來我們會如何進展現在還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是暫時還是會繼續這樣的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是在我家附近採的蘑菇和野菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為要到附近辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就打算順便送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是辦什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡有好多美味的食品店
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是把末續也叫來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那倒不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟她可是敵對關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用掃帚飛到天上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}騎著掃帚飛天？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬 到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要是小紅做的 什麼都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以啊…不要輕易就這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

